{{Quote|I'd do almost anything for a peek under that helmet...almost ''anything''.|A [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] stripper to [[Jango Fett/Legends|Jango Fett]]|<ref name="Star Wars: Jango Fett">[[Star Wars: Jango Fett (one-shot)|''Star Wars: Jango Fett'']]</ref>}}
A '''stripper''' was a type of [[Entertainer|dancer]] that specialized in sexual enticement. During a dance routine, the stripper would take off their outer garments in a stylistic fashion, revealing their underwear or semi-nude or nude forms.

During his time on [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]], [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Isolder]] imagined the many [[Witches of Dathomir|Dathomiri witches]] of [[Singing Mountain Clan]] staring at him with lust as though he were a stripper.

